data.title: Jack Redd - 2021 - Men's Soccer
data.meta_description:
Jack Redd (27) Midfielder  - Club/Prep Career
Member of club team that made three Nebraska State Cup Championships and four consecutive Nebraska League championships
data.text:
Club/Prep Career

Member of club team that made three Nebraska State Cup Championships and four consecutive Nebraska League championships ... Part of squad that earned the 2019 USCS Regional Championship and a spot in the USCS National semifinals ... Also member of 2019 Real Cup finalist squad ... Helped lead Papillion-La Vista South High School to the 2019 Nebraska State tournament ... Led the Titans in goals that season and earned Class A All-State honorable mention selection ... Claimed Region 2 ODP Regional Poll selection five times ... Earned selection to the 2019 Union Omaha USL Academy team ... Member of National Honor Society, Leadership Academy and DECA.

Personal

Son of Angi and Chris ... Has one sister, Dylan ... Currently undecided on his major.
